%livy2.spark

val renamePayment = deleteColumnPay.withColumnRenamed("Facility Name","Facility_Name").withColumnRenamed("Payment Measure ID","Payment_Measure_ID").withColumnRenamed("Start Date","Start_Date").withColumnRenamed("End Date","End_Date").withColumnRenamed("Higher Estimate", "Higher_Estimate").withColumnRenamed("Lower Estimate", "Lower_Estimate")

val replacePayment = renamePayment.withColumn(
    "Higher_Estimate",
    when(
        $"Higher_Estimate".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Higher_Estimate")).withColumn(
    "Lower_Estimate",
    when(
        $"Lower_Estimate".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Lower_Estimate")).withColumn(
    "Payment",
    when(
        $"Payment".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Payment")).withColumn(
    "Payment_Measure_ID",
    when(
        $"Payment_Measure_ID".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Payment_Measure_ID"))
        
val dropPayment = replacePayment.na.drop()

dropPayment.printSchema()
dropPayment.show(50)

%livy2.spark
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.expr

val replacePayment2 = dropPayment.withColumn("Higher_Estimate", regexp_replace($"Higher_Estimate",",","")).withColumn("Lower_Estimate", regexp_replace($"Lower_Estimate",",","")).withColumn("Payment", regexp_replace($"Payment",",",""))

val replacePayment3 = replacePayment2.withColumn("Higher_Estimate", expr("substring(Higher_Estimate, 2, length(Higher_Estimate))")).withColumn("Lower_Estimate", expr("substring(Lower_Estimate, 2, length(Lower_Estimate))")).withColumn("Payment", expr("substring(Payment, 2, length(Payment))"))

replacePayment3.show(100)

%livy2.spark
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.DoubleType

val convertPayment = replacePayment3.withColumn(
    "Higher_Estimate_Double",
    replacePayment3("Higher_Estimate").cast(DoubleType)).drop("Higher_Estimate").withColumnRenamed("Higher_Estimate_Double", "Higher_Estimate").withColumn(
    "Lower_Estimate_Double",
    replacePayment3("Lower_Estimate").cast(DoubleType)).drop("Lower_Estimate").withColumnRenamed("Lower_Estimate_Double", "Lower_Estimate").withColumn(
    "Payment_Double",
    replacePayment3("Payment").cast(DoubleType)).drop("Payment").withColumnRenamed("Payment_Double", "Payment")

convertPayment.printSchema()
convertPayment.show(100)
convertPayment.count()
